Package: mobdb
Type: Package
Title: Access the Mobility Database API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "A", , "me@jasonadle.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to search and access transit feed data from the 
    Mobility Database (mobilitydata.org). The package wraps the Mobility Database 
    API v1, allowing users to discover GTFS and GTFS Realtime feeds from transit 
    agencies worldwide. Functions are designed to integrate seamlessly with the 
    tidytransit and gtfstools packages for subsequent feed analysis.
